summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fremont Avenue from Kilbourne Street to North Fiftieth Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 15323, creating Local Improvement District No. 1410 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
